--- update --help ---
Update the Leo CLI

Usage: leo update [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -d                                 Print additional information for debugging
  -l, --list                         List all available releases.
  -n, --name <NAME>                  An optional release version, e.g. `vCURRENT`.
      --json-output[=<JSON_OUTPUT>]  Write command results as JSON. Pass `--json-output=<FILE>` for a custom path; with no value it defaults to build/json-outputs/<command>.json.
  -q, --quiet                        Suppress download logs.
      --disable-update-check         Disable Leo's daily check for version updates
      --path <PATH>                  Path to Leo program root folder
      --home <HOME>                  Path to aleo program registry
  -p, --package <PACKAGE>            Target a specific workspace member by name
  -h, --help                         Print help
